{"data":[{"id":561424669,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561424669","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545966625,"updated_time":1545967555,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"comment_count":8,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e我发现这个问题底下\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e回答里面觉得答题的人都恶意满满的主页点进去都是没有科研经历或者对理工科完全没概念的人，觉得应该对题主鼓励啊，应该鼓励创新，他还只是个孩子啊，又不会造成影响。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我想如果你如果天天搞科学研究到两点，为了一道数值问题会花几个小时，甚至只是为了装一个matlab就等了很久的人，当你看到这个问题和题主有关的回应时，内心应该和我一样愤怒。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我是一个数学本科的学生，曾经的我，也觉得自己特别聪明，对理工科也没有什么概念，我相信那个时候的我如果看到这个问题也会这么想，凭什么不给我们机会，凭什么说我们是错的；但是当我学习了数学的有关课程，数学分析，高等代数，偏微分方程，数值计算，实变函数这些科目的时候，那些头秃的日日夜夜，那些抓狂的瞬间。我现在非常能理解题目下那些说侮辱科学的人的心情，当你视之如珍宝的东西被别人这样践踏，你的心情只会比现在更愤怒。你没有了解科研工作者理工科的辛苦你又凭什么指责我们恶意满满呢？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e相反和我们一样理工科的知乎大v，他们就能理解我们的苦，但他们可能比我们考虑的周到，既提出了问题，也不乏劝告，可以说是很温暖的人了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ePS:题主我高中跟你心境差不多，但是也没想过解决哥猜这种问题，只觉得自己高考肯定能上清华北大，我也不像其他答主推荐你看什么数论了，毕竟数学本科到目前为止也没接触到，我建议你看一下华东师范的《数学分析》（都不用看苏联的卓里奇和菲赫金哥尔茨）这是数学系最最最基础的课程了，然后做一下吉米多维奇的习题，当然你觉得没必要拘泥于什么课本上的内容我也没办法，但是大厦不是一下建成的，基础必须得有。就算研究量子力学的科学家，他们对经典力学理解也是非常深的\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"我发现这个问题底下回答里面觉得答题的人都恶意满满的主页点进去都是没有科研经历或者对理工科完全没概念的人，觉得应该对题主鼓励啊，应该鼓励创新，他还只是个孩子啊，又不会造成影响。我想如果你如果天天搞科学研究到两点，为了一道数值问题会花几个小时…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=207\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoti